<!-- Abstract about this handbook -->

<abstract>
<para>
&kapp; is an application for simulating networks with boolean and Analog data 
types. String and other types are planned for the future. Currently there 
exists an array of basic components but because of the modular 
characteristics of KSimus, development of more components are easy. 
</para>
</abstract>

